metadata.name: The Gatekeeper
metadata.description:
The Gatekeeper isn't just a guardian - it's an embodiment of commitment and dedication. This artwork challenges you to prove your passion for the journey ahead, raising questions about what you're willing to sacrifice and how far you're ready to go in the pursuit of digital enlightenment.

Memetica is a collection of nine engravings, each representing a step on a mystical journey through the digital realm. These cryptic pieces are more than just art â€“ they form a complex puzzle waiting to be unraveled. Together, they hold the key to a hidden treasure. In Memetica, enlightenment and wealth await those daring enough to unravel its mysteries.
